-----------------
download balena etcher
download iso files for linux or ubuntu
choosing the PD run the balena etcher selecting the iso file and flash the PD
give a restart

-------------------
open the BIOS menu during restart by pressing DEL key
change the BIOS optin to legac
in security tab change secured boot to disable
save and exit using F10
-----------------
during restart open BOOT order using F11 key
select the PD
